name: 1:1 Potcorn
intro_text: Cannabis-infused microwave popcorn
short_description: Each bag uses Sea Salt and sustainably sourced organic palm oil to give it a lightly salted buttery flavor and contains approximately 5 mg CBD and 5 mg THC.
description:
Pop some harmony with our cannabis-infused microwave popcorn. Enjoy a bag of fresh and hot popcorn with a balanced dose of THC:CBD in every bite. Microwave bag contains 1 serving size. Gluten-free.
Pop-Up Potcorn uses Sea Salt and sustainably sourced organic palm oil to give it a lightly salted buttery flavor. Pop-Up Potcorn uses mini size, single serving microwave popcorn bags which make around 5 cups of popcorn. Traditional size microwave popcorn bags make around 12 cups of popcorn.
ingredients:
Popcorn, organic palm fruit oil, sea salt, cannabis oil. Cooking Instructions: Remove the popcorn bag from the exterior CR packaging before putting in the microwave to cook. The popcorn will cook on high for 1-2 minutes or once the kernels slow to 1-2 seconds per pop.

*Note: Do NOT use the popcorn setting on the microwave. Microwave ovens that have a popcorn setting are calibrated for a standard size popcorn bag and will most certainly burn the mini-size bag and shouldn’t be used.

Serving Method: Its best to empty the popcorn into a bowl in order to distribute the salt evenly. We like to hold the empty bag above the bowl with the opening facing down and rub the sides together to free the remaining salt from the bag.

Storage: Potcorn is best stored in a cool, dark environment, away from direct sunlight. The oil inside the bag has a melting point in the high 90’s and will start to “stain” or “sweat” from the paper popcorn bag when sits melted for an extended period of time. If the bag does stain or sweat it is still okay to pop and consume.
dosing:
1:1 – Approximately 5 mg CBD - 5 mg THC per Bag *Final dosing may vary slightly batch to batch

Pop-Up Potcorn is formulated so that 1 serving equals 1 bag and contains 10mg of distillate. Consumers who are familiar with their dosing will be able to choose accordingly between our 3 formulations. For consumers who are not, we suggest starting with the CBD only or the 1:1 ratio bag.
internal_name: - 1:1 Potcorn

name: Rainbow Sherbet Limited Edition Pride Gummies
intro_text: Celebrate Pride with these limited edition sativa gummies.
short_description: Celebrate Pride with PLUS! Made with an uplifting Sativa blend, each perfectly dosed gummy contains 5mg of THC. A portion of proceeds will be donated to the San Francisco-based Transgender, Gender-Variant & Intersex Justice Project.
description:
Celebrate Pride with PLUS! Our best-selling limited edition Pride Rainbow Sherbet gummy is back for the 4th year in a row. Made with an uplifting Sativa blend, each perfectly dosed gummy contains 5mg of THC. What makes these gummies even sweeter? For every tin sold PLUS will donate a portion of proceeds to the San Francisco-based Transgender, Gender-Variant & Intersex Justice Project (TGIJP) to further their mission of ending the human rights abuses committed against Black and Brown TGI people inside of California prisons, jails, detention centers and beyond. Elevate your mood and join the celebration with this festive limited edition flavor!
Queer rights are civil rights, and we can’t elevate and celebrate the message of Pride without elevating and celebrating the Black, Brown and trans voices that founded - and continue to lead - the fight for dignity, life and equality for all.

Why Celebrate Pride with PLUS

This year, PLUS is donating a portion of proceeds from each Pride tin sold to the San Francisco-based Transgender, Gender-Variant & Intersex Justice Project (TGIJP). For over 16 years, TGIJP has been working to end human rights abuses against transgender, gender-variant and intersex people in California prisons and beyond, particularly ensuring the safety and empowerment of Black trans women and folks. To learn more or donate, please visit www.tgijp.org.

A New Look

Inspired by the Progress Pride Flag’s emphasis on inclusion and progression, PLUS Pride packaging now includes the white, pink, and light blue colors of the transgender flag, while the brown and black stripes represent people of color.

What’s Inside

PLUS Limited Edition Pride Rainbow Sherbet gummies are made with an uplifting Sativa blend. Each perfectly dosed gummy contains 5mg of THC so elevate your mood and join the celebration with this festive limited-edition flavor!
ingredients: Glucose, sucrose, kosher gelatin, sorbitol, citric acid, natural and artificial flavoring, erythrosine, cannabis. May contain trace amounts of mineral oil.
dosing: Approximately 0 mg CBD - 100 mg THC per tin | 0 mg CBD - 5 mg THC per serving. Exact dosage will vary batch to batch.
internal_name: Plus - Rainbow Sherbet Limited Edition Pride Gummies

A Chemistry CCELL battery is the best match for your Chemistry CCELL cartridge--and most other 510 thread cartridges! What Is CCELL Technology?

The absolute best pocketable vaporizer technology available on the market. Hands down. Not even debatable. Internally, we call it a “dabstick."

intro_text: An acid-rich 5:1 botanical formula made with raw Moon Made Farms flower rosin.
short_description: Made with infusions of nettle, olive leaf, passionflower and cramp bark (some grown on our family farm), this multi-herb tincture contains immune boosting, mood lifting and anti-inflammatory properties that target a number of female health concerns.
description:
A 5:1 acid-rich women’s health formula made with Moon Made Farms flower rosin, this product is the truest expression of full spectrum plant medicine. Made with infusions of nettle, olive leaf, passionflower and cramp bark (some grown on our family farm), this multi-herb tincture contains immune boosting, mood lifting and anti-inflammatory properties that target a number of female health concerns. This CBD/A-rich tincture contains a therapeutic dose of THCA and THC and is for women of all ages. Strains are Moon Made Farm’s Super CBD and Pineapple Wonder, which have uplifting, mood boosting, energizing and anti-inflammatory properties.
Benefits of Inner Balance include:

• Powerful and fast acting anti-inflammatory for instant relief and to manage inflammation throughout the month. Aids in inflammatory conditions such as painful periods, endometriosis and hot flashes. 
• Calms the nervous system and has been effective in individuals suffering from acute anxiety, migraines and other stress conditions
• CBD and passionflower have mood stabilizing properties
• Nettle and olive leaf contain powerful antioxidants
• Nettle promotes urinary tract health 
• Olive leaf supports a healthy immune system

This product is Sun + Earth Certified. This certification means that this cannabis is grown under the sun, in the soil of mother earth, without chemicals, by fairly paid farmers.
ingredients:
Holistically farmed California cold-pressed, extra virgin olive oil, Sun + Earth certified regeneratively grown sun-grown cannabis flower rosin, nettle, passionflower, crampbark and olive leaf.
All ingredients are sustainably farmed and holistically processed. Sonoma County olive oil is currently undergoing Oregon Tilth certification.

May be mildly psychoactive.
dosing: Approximately 101.1 mg CBD - 24.3 mg THC - 157.5 mg CBDA - 26.1 mg THCA per 30 ml bottle. Start with a 1/4 dropperful under tongue; hold for 30 seconds. Wait 30 minutes before increasing dose. Store in a cool, dry place, away from sunlight.

name: Renewing Serum
intro_text: Face Serum for Normal to Dry Skin
short_description: An improvement of the original High CBD Healing Serum. This super moisturizing, antioxidant-rich serum is loaded with anti-inflammatory power for normal to dry skin.
description:
We’ve improved our award-winning original serum (formerly “High CBD Healing Serum”) by adding a potent, stable form of vitamin C for its antioxidant and collagen-boosting celebrity status. Formulated for normal to dry skin, this super moisturizing serum is loaded with antioxidants and anti-inflammatory power to help smooth fine lines, brighten and balance skin tone, hydrate and protect against environmental damage.
Cannabis-based serums are able to penetrate multiple epidermis layers and bind with our skin’s natural endocannabinoid receptors, sealing in all the juicy goodness for the most intensive results. Made of organic exotic essential oils, blue tansy flowers, vitamin C, vitamin E, and THC and CBD in a 1:1 ratio, this facial serum has a light and uplifting scent and silky texture. This little ounce of prevention is worth its weight in (cannabis) gold.

  • WINNER, Best Topical, 2018 California-wide Cannabis Competition
  • Non-psychoactive
  • Made with clean, whole-plant, full-spectrum cannabis
  • Purity, potency and regulatory compliance verified by Cannalysis Labs
  • 98% organic ingredients
ingredients:
Simmondsia chinensis (jojoba) oil*, Prunus armeniaca (apricot) kernel oil*, Olea europea (squalane) oil, Corylus avellana (hazelnut) oil*, Argania spinosa (argan) oil*, tetrahexyldecyl ascorbate (vitamin C), Cannabis sativa extract, tocopherol (vitamin E), Citrus sinensis (orange) essential oil*, Tanacetum annuum (blue tansy) essential oil*, Ocimum basilicum (basil) essential Oil*, Commiphora myrrha (myrrh) essential oil*
*organically grown
dosing:
38 mg CBD - 38 mg THC
1 oz

How to use:

A little dab’ll do ya: After cleansing and toning, add one pump of Renewing Serum into your palm and lightly stir with your fingertips to warm it up. Gently pat onto your face, neck and décolletage. When using additional face products — moisturizers, makeup, sunscreen, etc. — make sure to apply this serum first. Use morning and night.

For external use only. Keep out of the reach of children and pets. If pregnant, nursing or under a doctor’s care, consult a physician before use.
internal_name: Green Bee Botanicals - Renewing Serum

short_description: These limited edition delights are made with Pure Beauty's Harlequin x GDP, a beautiful 1:1 CBD strain. Magical Grapes strain have you feeling lucid without being overstimulated and cozy without relegating you to the couch.
description:
Chef Dominique Crenn’s first curated chef: Virgilio Martínez Véliz of Centrale Restaurant in Lima, Peru, created a gorgeous flavor combining a grape juice we’d made from our friends Seiji & Chiho Morimoto’s Shinano Smile Japanese grapes with cold-infused muddled ginger and crushed pink peppercorn. The flavor is the perfect balance of spicy and juicy, with the spices really highlighting the fragrance of the Shinano Smile grapes. The box’s design is inspired by Seiji & Chiho’s love of tie-dye and their family-run farm, Magical Grapes, in Ventura.
Edition of 1180 hand-numbered boxes.

Made with Pure Beauty's Harlequin x GDP, a beautiful 1:1 CBD strain, this strain will have you feeling lucid without being overstimulated and cozy without relegating you to the couch. A sweet nose, with hints of fruit, and a dense bud structure make this strain easy on the eyes, nose and mind, as you feel all anxiety melt away.
ingredients: Grapes, water, cane sugar, tapioca syrup, non-gmo potato starch, MCT coconut oil, non-gmo citric acid, cannabis flower rosin, ginger, pink peppercorn, kosher salt. Coating: tapioca starch, powdered sugar.
dosing: Approximately 2.8 mg CBD - 2.4 mg THC per piece | 56 mg CBD - 58 mg THC per box. 20 Delights per box. Exact dosing may vary from batch to batch.

The 4 oz size is perfectly portable and infused with 10 mg* of pure THC so you can throw it into your bag and sip it, spike it, or shoot it anytime you need a boost. We designed our coffee to help improve mood and to enhance a sense of well-being. Our infused coffee is faster acting and more bioavailable than other edibles giving you a clear and euphoric mind and relaxed body. The hybrid THC, combined with the naturally-occurring caffeine from the coffee, gives a more Sativa-leaning feel.
ingredients: Filtered water, Organic Coffee, butane-free THC, vegan protein (used for cannabis infusion) (No Sugar! Each bottle is only 2 calories)
dosing:
Size 4 fl oz | 10 mg Hybrid THC | Keep refrigerated Suggested Dose: We recommend new patients start with ½ a bottle for approximately 5 mg. Patients may start feeling effects as quickly as 20 minutes, and because of our increased bioavailability the effect may be greater than a typical 10 mg dose.

Somatik™ is ready to drink and best served chilled from the bottle or over ice. If you want to mix it up, combine it with your favorite milk, add a shot to a morning smoothie, or pour some into your regular cup of coffee for a morning boost. Bottles should be stored in a refrigerator and drunk within 3-5 day of being opened.

Testing results may vary slightly as labs continue to perfect their ability to accurately test low-dose beverages. By law we are required to list dose based on non-optimized results — occasionally as a lower dose. However we encourage you to treat this is a 10 mg drink and dose it accordingly. This drink is more bio-available and faster acting than any other edible and we want you to have the perfect experience, so go slow!

categories: Shop/Products/Inhale/Pax Era Pods,Shop/Explore/Cannabinoids/THC,Shop/Explore/Cannabinoids/CBD,Shop/Explore/Strain/Hybrid/Indica-Dominant,Shop/Explore/Strain/Indica,Shop/Explore/Helps With/Anxiety,Shop/Explore/Helps With/Mood,Shop/Explore/Helps With/Sleep,Shop/Explore/Helps With/Stress,Shop/Explore/Helps With/Creativity,Shop/Explore/Feeling/Nighttime
name: Northern Lights Single Origin Pax Era Pod
intro_text: Otherworldly indica to deliver creativity and to soothe the body.
short_description: Deeply earthy and piney with herbal notes that recall bay leaves, Northern Lights delivers legendary potency to uplift the mind with focused creativity and soothe the body with heavily numbing comfort.
description:
Enjoy an otherworldly experience with this hazy hybrid that comes on quickly and compels you to sit back, relax and smile. Deeply earthy and piney with herbal notes that recall bay leaves, Northern Lights delivers legendary potency to uplift the mind with focused creativity and soothe the body with heavily numbing comfort. Northern Lights is one of the most famous and sought-after “Indica” strains of all time. Considered a descendant of Afghani and Thai landrace strains, the exact origin of Northern Lights remains a bit of a mystery. It may have originated in Washington in the 1970s, prior to reaching the Netherlands, where breeder Neville Schoenmaker pioneered several Northern Lights phenotypes in the ’80s for The Seed Bank, an early iteration of Sensi Seeds.

Since 1985, when Sensi Seeds first commercialized this strain, Northern Lights has been a landmark Indica strain in cannabis culture. Northern Lights #5 — arguably the most popular Northern Lights phenotype — won the Cannabis Cup in 1989, 1990, and 1992. Sensi Seeds currently offers feminized, non-feminized, and autoflowering Northern Lights seeds.
internal_name: Bloom Farms - Northern Lights Single Origin Pax Era Pod

name: 1:1 Releaf Patch
intro_text: 1:1 transdermal cannabis patch for acute discomfort and aches.
short_description: Transdermal Releaf patches offer up to 12 hours of measured and effective whole-body comfort. Made with fresh-pressed Cannabis rosin, these slow-release patches are great for alleviating acute discomfort or muscle soreness after a long workout.
description:
text in italicPapa & Barkley’s transdermal Releaf patches offer up to 12 hours of measured and effective whole-body comfort. Made with fresh-pressed Cannabis rosin, these slow-release patches are chemical-free and great for alleviating acute discomfort or muscle soreness after a long workout. Key Benefits

  • Slow release of cannabinoids for consistent effects that last up to 12 hours
  • Transdermal (meaning cannabinoids slowly absorb into the skin) to provide both topical relief and internal benefits simultaneously
  • Long-lasting relief from discomfort and minor aches

How It’s Made

  • Handcrafted with fresh-pressed Cannabis rosin to maintain the whole plant profile with the full spectrum of cannabinoids, terpenes and phytonutrients
  • Fresh-pressed using only heat – no solvents or chemicals used in the process
  • Infused oil is precisely applied to each patch using modified 3D printing technology
ingredients: Cannabis, Menthol, Camphor, Methyl Salicylate, Mineral Oil, Oleic Acid.
dosing:
1:1 CBD:THC
Apply the patch to clean skin that is free of hair and moisture. To use the patch, remove the protective liner on the patch and place the sticky side down onto your skin. Press firmly. Recommended application areas: Inside of wrists, inside/outside of biceps, shoulders, back of neck, back, ankle.

Duration: up to 12 hours Onset time: 1 hour +/- 30 min. Starting dose: 1 patch Preferred by individuals with: whole body aches or acute discomfort
internal_name: Papa & Barkley - 1:1 Releaf Patch

Papa & Barkley’s transdermal Releaf patches offer up to 12 hours of measured and effective whole-body comfort. Made with fresh-pressed Cannabis rosin, these slow-release patches are chemical-free and great for alleviating acute discomfort or muscle soreness after a long workout. Key Benefits

Papaya is an indica-dominant hybrid cannabis strain that is known for producing mental calmness, though many consumers also find that this strain makes them energetic and productive. Nirvana Seeds bred this to be their take on a Mango strain and crossed Citral #13 with Ice #2 to make their own fruit. They met their own challenge and Papaya smells uncannily like its namesake. The taste is similar to its tropical fruit counterpart, but a spicy, peppery side also becomes apparent. Papa's Select makes California's premier award-winning solventless Living Extracts. We use only top-tier cannabis that has been grown in the world's renowned cannabis region, the Emerald Triangle. Our products provide the truest expression of these plants by only introducing water and heat to the extraction process. Papa’s Select products are considered Living Extracts because they are made with cannabis that has been frozen moments after being harvested, while the cannabis flowers are still fresh and at peak ripeness. This process allows us to unlock the potential of the plant at the perfect moment in time and provide the best possible product to our consumers.

Key Benefits

  • Made with chemical-free process: uses only ice, water, heat, and pressure.
  • Unrivaled flavor and terpene profile.
  • High potency and full spectrum of cannabinoids.
  • Captures the complete profile of the plant.

How It’s Made Made with cannabis that has been frozen moments after being harvested, while the cannabis flowers are still fresh and at peak ripeness. Our process uses only ice, water, heat, and pressure to create the cleanest form of cannabis concentrates. Solventless extracts are different than solvent-free extracts, which use a chemical aid in the extraction process that is later purged out.
